            <title>[SYNAPSE-579] Generating a unique name for annonymous endpoints</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-579</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If a unique name is not specified anonymous endpoints will not work in a clustered environment. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
